name: Swayam Sevika Report
query:
SELECT 
    employee_id AS `Employee ID`, 
    CONCAT(emp_first_name, ' ', emp_last_name) AS `Employee Name`, 
    designation AS `Designation`, 
    region AS `Region`, 
    branch AS `Branch`, 
    ss_code AS `SS Code`,  
    full_name AS `Swayam Sevika Name`,
    city AS `City`
FROM 
    `tabSwayam Sevika Data`
ORDER BY
    CAST(employee_id AS UNSIGNED) ASC;
